{"tid":1352220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"馬照跑 舞照跳","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T18:16:04.000Z","uid":114478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3cc098fac126acb1b01bfb649bfb29843cbdad","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"兄弟<br />\n諗清楚喇，人地老黑打鳩你，就係想你驚<br />\n我地要做既，就係好似平時咁，唔撚驚，平時係點，就做返平時，佢地短時間唔會亂黎。<br />\n夢遊去左支聯，搞到志民嬲豬，應該繼續做，到地區有事，咪即撒，再轉場幫拖。<br />\n琴晚其中一個誤判就係冇去元朗即時back up，古惑仔都係人，人多就會驚<br />\n倒轉諗野，仲有機會贏。而家秒殺老黑只會勞民傷財，差佬已經難搞，仲要打佢地既合體版本，同送頭有咩分別？"},{"pid":"cab1a623967b24f024e25250dd9b55887d0fb13b","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"32c264ebd8c7115dfe3bee9be1b3c09799c7c9a3","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06238cdb5cf4504834eaae536540076fb6a22ed3","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1495154c013b942388f76ee1d502f6962340b4","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bab262b589a5acd41820ec4c7bd017f99b1e835","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"達狗19post就係咁推<br />\n認真野又唔撚睇<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"c524e056937d2a652462c38a889fdf3104998918","tid":1352220,"uid":114478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}